Cauliflower Tots
  --delish

4 c cauliflower florets, steamed (~1/2 large cauliflower)
1 large egg, lightly beaten
1 c shredded cheddar
1 c freshly grated parmesan
2/3 c panko
1/4 c finely chopped chives
kosher salt
freshly ground black pepper
1/2 c ketchup
2 tbsp sriracha

In a food processor, pulse the steamed cauliflower until grated. Place grated cauliflower on a clean kitchen towel and squeeze to drain water from cauliflower. Transfer to a large bowl and add egg, cheeses, panko, and chives. Mix until combined. Season with salt and pepper to taste. Spoon ~1 tbsp mixture and roll into a tater tot shape with your hands. Working in batches, arrange tots in single layer in air fryer basket and cook at 375F for 10 min, until tots are golden. Mix ketchup and sriracha in a small bowl and set aside for serving with tots.
